cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

This paper discusses the automation of neural architecture search, which is a topic that falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the focus is on deep learning and neural architecture search, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely categories, followed by cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.CL.
